{"tid":1701093,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（心理戰術） 羞辱個別警員","createTime":"2019-11-09T00:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T02:12:04.000Z","uid":42751,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16341d4df858be116b294d52cb5390cb967e4efd","tid":1701093,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:05:37.000Z","msg":"要分化班狗根本冇難度， 當你見到一堆警察嘅時候， 大叫： 傷心柴～～升職未呀～～～ 17年喇喎～～ 仲未見broad 呀？ 你隔離啲夥記都恥笑你升唔到職呀～～ 你望下佢哋嘅表情～～ 早啲返去溫書啦～ 唔好再做一柴喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算當時冇嘢，返到局入邊佢地心入邊都會睇唔起呢一個高級警員， 有一班警察嘅時候根本一定會有一兩件傷心柴， 呢個地圖砲萬試萬靈， 有幾次班狗撤退嘅時候有人咁樣問侯班狗， 即刻有兩個好心虛咁樣擰轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a63c30353c547efba33bb3bd4e9a108f53a3082","tid":1701093,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37323e7d9f7957248d4e180a6e78d1add6fefffb","tid":1701093,"uid":82639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ecda90daa6122342e65773ef6904dae4285713b","tid":1701093,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:40:36.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"26d1e34ff6e4415fa4fc3fdf2aadad56ca828d83","tid":1701093,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:03:14.000Z","msg":"👍🏿👍🏿"},{"pid":"5d06d817e668d1ac9e107e276d14a3d7167a37ae","tid":1701093,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:06:37.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"20cb9d4a4254fe18f5ce486907259f615919ab47","tid":1701093,"uid":7524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-